{"tid":189580,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人真係見證過迴光反照?","createTime":"2017-04-06T13:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T15:22:50.000Z","uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a9989ae52b52d43ab5dd527ba4a710ca5af1d6","tid":189580,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"姐係類似一個病人昏迷左好耐或者食藥食到迷迷糊糊左好耐 總知情況比較差啦<br />\n突然之間有一日好精神 可以同屋企人傾下偈 記得番以前好多野 甚至開開心心食埋飯飲埋茶咁<br />\n但結果個一晚或者過兩日就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想聽多啲呢類型既故事"},{"pid":"e730cc3267a5de216fefd0b8a7498b2c769bd0ef","tid":189580,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"係講好左數<br />\n<br />\n比返預定時間佢"},{"pid":"6d3ff441f99afa8f59874a8b497ead5b80ac3325","tid":189580,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:11:19.000Z","msg":"成日見<br />\n不過唔係個個人都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba11439bf8fbe43f16fbc0b9074640f77434652a","tid":189580,"uid":2839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日見<br />\n不過唔係個個人都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解成日見?? 你係醫院做野??"},{"pid":"b1232ced92f41f2eed348def8d6062a7f7972845","tid":189580,"uid":2839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"我女朋友隻貓臨死前, 突然好精神咁圍住屋企行左一個圈, 之後訓左落我女友手臂先過身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20915b4dd8cc1f4bb5a43f033307693216654f00","tid":189580,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"人就唔知<br />\n我認真講既以下 唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前養狗 晚年佢都唔點郁（14歲）<br />\n有一晚佢好活躍 跑黎跑去 有精神好多咁<br />\n之後我就出左街 <br />\n出到一半收到家人電話 佢死左<br />\n我返去睇 